test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [-2] == [-2, -2]
  Right contains one more item: -2
  Full diff:
  - [-2, -2]
  + [-2]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0, 0] == [0, 0]
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0]
  + [0, 0, 0]
  ?     +++
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [] == [2]
  Right contains one more item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2]
  ?  -
  + []
